保障」，表示中方支持一切有利于和平的努力，释放哪些信号？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "4 月 2 日，外交部发言人毛宁主持例行记者会。 有外媒记者提问，有报道称，伊朗已向中国寻求安全保障，如果这些保障能够提供，美以伊或能达成停火协议。请问伊朗是否已向中国提出过此类请求？中国是否已作出回应？ 「伊朗战事爆发以来，中方一直积极致力于促和止战，中巴两国外长会见的情况，我们已经发布了消息，你可以查阅。」毛宁说，我可以告诉你的是，中方支持一切有利于和平的努力，我们也愿意同各方加强沟通和协调，为恢复中东地区的和平继续发挥作用。 外媒称伊朗已向中国寻求安全保障，外交部回应"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-361546b71010d594e66082919922bcb4.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "94 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2023064985580893986"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIuPfcn+iQqKESEAMaCTExODk5NjYzMSD3v7jOBjAAOJwFQApyEzIwMjMwNjQ5ODU1ODA4OTM5ODZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1775230757.693541", "card_id": "Q_1947271556913934593", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 25}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "和牛的牛杂卖给哪里了？还是直接扔了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "牛内脏 牛眼睛 牛枪牛宝 牛舌头之类的"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-46ada2cc4f43bdea5b64acb4482241e2_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "92 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1947271556913934593"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIuPfcn+iQqKESEAMaCTExNjQ3ODEzMCDVx+nFBjAAOExAC3ITMTk0NzI3MTU1NjkxMzkzNDU5M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1775230757.693785", "card_id": "Q_2023331246357357393", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "教育部启动 2026 年中小学阳光招生专项行动，严禁设立或变相设立重点班，还有那些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "教育部今天（3 日）发布通知，启动实施 2026 年中小学阳光招生专项行动，不断健全公平公开、规范透明、监管有力的长效机制。 据了解，2024 、 2025 年，教育部已连续两年部署开展义务教育阳光招生专项行动，但部分地方、部分学校在学区划片调整、特定类型招生、均衡分班等关键环节还存在不足之处。今年，专项行动全面升级，首次将普通高中招生全面纳入专项行动，贯通义务教育与高中阶段治理链条。过去，专项行动侧重于对招生环节的规范，今年将统筹推进资源前瞻布局、招生行为规范、均衡编班管理、风险防控保障，构建起覆盖招生全流程、全要素的系统治理框架。 更多资讯请下载央视新闻客户端"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/100/v2-e7bb12bf792c5b2a62a1b7e4b5ea1ff5_r.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "69 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2023331246357357393"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIuPfcn+iQqKESEAMaCTExOTAwNDE1MyDwr7zOBjAAOEVADHITMjAyMzMzMTI0NjM1NzM1NzM5M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1775230757.694493", "card_id": "Q_647797875", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1012}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "存款多少才能不上班？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-5dec2e8c585bb5e4fde3dbc43b0db2be_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "69 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/647797875"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIuPfcn+iQqKESEAMaCTEwNjIzMjM2OSD9y7GvBjAAOIQXQA1yCTY0Nzc5Nzg3NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1775230757.694834", "card_id": "Q_2023487705594565971", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 140}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "乒乓世界杯 1/8 决赛，王楚钦最终以 4 比 2 战胜小勒布伦，如何评价本场比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-f3120635c5e4ea0831f81d724edeefa6_720w.webp?